tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE WebsiteTrafficData (
  visitor_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  page_visited VARCHAR(255),
  visit_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  visitor_location VARCHAR(100),
  visitor_device VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE dashboard_data (
    dashboard_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    dashboard_name VARCHAR,
    widget_type VARCHAR,
    data_source VARCHAR,
    last_updated TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE website_visitors (
	visitor_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	visitor_name VARCHAR(255),
	visit_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
	page_visited VARCHAR(255),
	referrer_page VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE website_visits (
    visit_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    visitor_id INT,
    visit_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    page_visited VARCHAR(255)
)

CREATE TABLE visitor_details (
    visitor_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    visitor_name VARCHAR(100),
    visitor_location VARCHAR(100),
    visit_count INT
)

CREATE TABLE page_details (
    page_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    page_name VARCHAR(255),
    page_url VARCHAR(255),
    page_views INT
)

CREATE TABLE dashboard_data (
    dashboard_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    dashboard_name VARCHAR(100),
    dashboard_type VARCHAR(50),
    data_source VARCHAR(255)
)

CREATE TABLE website_visits (
    visit_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    visitor_ip VARCHAR(255),
    visit_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    page_visited VARCHAR(255),
    referral_source VARCHAR(255)
)

CREATE TABLE visitor_details (
    visitor_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    visitor_name VARCHAR(255),
    visitor_email VARCHAR(255),
    visitor_country VARCHAR(255),
    visit_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (visit_id) REFERENCES website_visits(visit_id)
)

CREATE TABLE page_views (
    view_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    visit_id INT,
    page_viewed VARCHAR(255),
    time_spent_seconds INT,
    UNIQUE (view_id, visit_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (visit_id) REFERENCES website_visits(visit_id)
)

CREATE TABLE user_accounts (
    user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    username VARCHAR(255) UNIQUE,
    email VARCHAR(255) UNIQUE,
    registration_date TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE dashboard_logs (
    log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    action_performed VARCHAR(255),
    log_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES user_accounts(user_id)
)
